hopobject.body: I have my own business unipharm lebanon owner Even the higher of those prices is not unrealistic, according to another manager. “The current target price, based on our model of the business, is north of £5,” said the manager, who declined to be named. “That is assuming only a small improvement in profit margins from current levels. By 2015 this business should be making more than £500m of profits.” The current figure is nearer £400m.
